When start set the time to 00:00

When press start do the loop for pomodoro clock
	Study -> rest -> Study -> rest -> ...
	if press start again pause the time
	if press end end this pomodoro session
	if press config do nothing
	if press mode do nothing

When press end do nothing

When press config
	show the Study time
	if press start increase the time
	if press end decrease the time
	if press config again then confirm the time
	if press mode change from Study -> rest time, rest -> Study timee

When press mode
	change mode accordingly
